Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:34.00,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}目光相汇的涟漪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:39.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}是和你之间的交流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:45.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}在这片蔚蓝之海上联系着的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:51.20,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}光之信标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:57.50,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}是否遇到了温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:23:03.00,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}现在的我有在笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:08.70,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}繁星照耀的寂寞眼瞳里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:13.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}洒满了光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:19.25,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}I'm close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:25.40,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}永远在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:30.56,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}即便是看不见明天的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:36.65,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}也会用心灵呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:41.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}Please,stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.10,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}请务必不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:58.10,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}直到能够牵手迎接日出的早晨
